sources.title: Something Beneath | FULL MOVIE | 2007 | Horror, Sci FI | Kevin Sorbo
sources.description:
A massive cellular organism, highly intelligent and deadly, is living in the sewer system beneath a conference center. As attendees of the Clean Planet conference are picked off one by one, a group of scientists band together to stop the ooze in its tracks.

Kevin Sorbo, Natalie Brown, Brendan Beiser, Peter MacNeill, Brittany Scobie, Blake Taylor, Tom Keenan

Directed by David Winning
2007

metadata.Plot: Beneath the facade, is fear. Beneath the smile, is shame. Beneath the ground... is death. Environmental activist Father Douglas Middleton (Kevin Sorbo, as a most unusual priest) must stop a primeval beast preying on his eco-conference colleagues -- or fall victim to it himself.
